41  import fr.mcc.ginco.beans.Language;

46  /**
47   * View class corresponding to {@link ThesaurusTerm} bean, but fully serializable;
48   * contains all links to other business-objects (full beans
49   * {@link Thesaurus} and {@link Language}).
50   * 
51   * @see fr.mcc.ginco.beans
52   */
53  @JsonIgnoreProperties({ "hibernateLazyInitializer", "handler" })
54  public class ThesaurusTermView implements Serializable {
55  	private String identifier;
56  	private String lexicalValue;
57  	private String created;
58  	private String modified;
59  	private String source;
60  	private Boolean prefered;
61  	private Boolean hidden;
62  	private Integer status;
63  	private String conceptId;
64  	private String thesaurusId;
65  	private String language;
66  	private String role;
67  
68  
69      public ThesaurusTermView() {}
70  
71  	public ThesaurusTermView(ThesaurusTerm source) {
72  		if (source != null) {
73  			this.identifier = source.getIdentifier();
74  			this.lexicalValue = source.getLexicalValue();
75  			if(source != null) {
76  				this.created = DateUtil.toString(source.getCreated());
77  				this.modified = DateUtil.toString(source.getModified());
78  			}
79              this.source = source.getSource();
80              this.prefered = source.getPrefered();
81              this.hidden = source.getHidden();
82              this.status = source.getStatus();
83              
84              if(source.getConcept() != null) {
85                  this.conceptId = source.getConcept().getIdentifier();
86              }
87  
88      		this.thesaurusId = source.getThesaurus().getIdentifier();
89      		if(source.getLanguage() != null) {
90      		this.language = source.getLanguage().getId();
91      		if (source.getRole() != null) {
92      			this.role = source.getRole().getCode();
93      		}
94      		}
95  		}
96  	}
97
